    "text": "可是斜坡如果造得越平緩的話",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 116.67,
    "end": 119.97,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "我們就要走越長越遠的路耶",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 120.17,
    "end": 125.38,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "沒錯 這就是所謂的省力必費時",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0,
    "commands": []
  },
  {
    "start": 125.58,
    "end": 149.04,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "③ $\\text{輪與平緩斜面} \\rightarrow \\text{省力但費時}$",
